              <img
                alt="testimonial"
                class="profile-img w-24 h-24 mb-8 object-cover object-center rounded-full inline-block border-2 border-gray-200 bg-gray-100"
                src="/assets/images/Sagar.jpg"
                style="box-shadow: 5px 5px 2px lightgreen;"
              />
              <p class="leading-relaxed">
                Highly passionate and energetic <strong>DevOps</strong> engineer
                with a strong background in infrastructure development and
                <strong
                  >CICD (Continuous Integration/Continuous Deployment)</strong
                >
                cycles. Enthusiastic and focused on enjoying life while
                completing responsibilities.
              </p>
              <span
                class="inline-block h-1 w-10 rounded bg-green-500 mt-6 mb-4"
              ></span>
              <h2
                class="text-gray-900 font-medium title-font tracking-wider text-sm"
              >
                SAGAR MEMANE
              </h2>
              <p class="text-gray-500">Project Member 1</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="lg:w-1/3 lg:mb-0 mb-6 p-4">
            <div class="h-full text-center">
              <img
                alt="testimonial"
                class="profile-img w-24 h-24 mb-8 object-cover object-center rounded-full inline-block border-2 border-gray-200 bg-gray-100"
                src="/assets/images/shital.jpeg"
                style="box-shadow: 5px 5px 2px lightgreen;"
              />
              <p class="leading-relaxed">
                Adaptable
                <strong>MSC IT student at Mumbai University</strong> with a
                background in <strong>civil defense</strong>. Quick learner with
                a patient approach, blending tech expertise with leadership
